detail.description: FSN E-commerce Ventures Ltd. (FSNEV) popularly known as "Nykaa" is a digitally native consumer technology platform, delivering a content-led, lifestyle retail experience to consumers. The company has a diverse portfolio of beauty, personal care, and fashion products, including owned brand products manufactured by it.[1]
